OL,3,CMurder victim's mum in Westminster for
OL,4,Ccrucial stage of fight to change law
OL,6,FThe mother of nine-year-old Olivia
OL,7,FPratt-Korbel, who was killed in her
OL,8,Fown home in Liverpool, has travelled
OL,9,Fto Westminster to see her campaign to
OL,10,Fchange the law in her daughter's name
OL,11,Freach a crucial stage.
OL,13,FOlivia's Law would seek to compel
OL,14,Fpeople convicted of serious offences
OL,15,Fto appear in court when they are being
OL,16,Fsentenced.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
