OL,3,CMurder victim's mum in Westminster for
OL,4,Ccrucial stage of fight to change law
OL,6,FOlivia was killed when drug dealer
OL,7,FThomas Cashman fired at a rival, who
OL,8,Fwas trying to force his way into her
OL,9,Fhome in Dovecot in August 2022. Her
OL,10,Fmother Cheryl was injured, but the
OL,11,Fsame bullet struck Olivia a fatal
OL,12,Finjury in her chest.
OL,14,FOther high-profile cases where
OL,15,Foffenders were absent from sentencing
OL,16,Finclude serial child killer Lucy
OL,17,FLetby, law graduate Zara Aleena's
OL,18,Fmurderer Jordan McSweeney, and primary
OL,19,Fschool teacher Sabina Nessa's killer
OL,20,FKoci Selamaj.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
