OL,3,CMurder victim's mum in Westminster for
OL,4,Ccrucial stage of fight to change law
OL,6,F"It means a lot and it's not just for
OL,7,Four family - it's for other families
OL,8,Fthat have got to do the same thing and
OL,9,Fhopefully it will be stopped and
OL,10,Fthey(defendants who refuse to come to
OL,11,Fcourt) will be coming up and facing
OL,12,Fwhat they need to face."
OL,14,FOlivia's aunt, Antonia Elverson,
OL,15,Fspeaking of the Bill one day becoming
OL,16,Flaw, added: "It's everything we've
OL,17,Ffought for - it's everything that's
OL,18,Fright."
